org.ietf.nea.pa.message

Class PaMessageHeaderBuilderIetf

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ietf.nea.pa.message.PaMessageHeaderBuilderIetf
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ImMessageHeaderBuilder, TransmissionObjectBuilder<ImMessageHeader>, PaMessageHeaderBuilder

    public class PaMessageHeaderBuilderIetf
extends Object
implements PaMessageHeaderBuilder
    Builder to build an integrity measurement component message header compliant to RFC 5792. It evaluates the given values and can be used in a fluent way.
